  "2026-06-07T07:41:48.128Z",codex-5.3-full-cycle,"Hardening pass complete: release:check succeeded after dependency bump and changelog regeneration."
  "2026-06-07T08:00:43.625Z",codex-5.3-full-cycle,"Security gate: high-confidence token/key regex scan over tracked files and git history found no actionable secrets. Binary-history false positives were traced to embedded wasm base64 blobs, not credentials."
  "2026-06-09T19:30:56.898Z",unknown,"2026-06-09 continuation: auditing all pm package repos for TypeScript-only implementation, current pm CLI/SDK and pm-changelog usage, release workflow readiness, GitHub alerts/PRs/issues, secret/history hygiene, and real-data functional checks. Constraints: do not modify pm-cli repo except GitHub issues; do not modify telemetry/observability setup; avoid duplicate pm items; use existing hardening wave item as coordination record."
  "2026-06-09T19:43:48.311Z",unknown,"2026-06-09 verification update: active /pm-packages release:check sweep passed for pm-beads, pm-changelog, pm-csv, pm-gantt-chart, pm-github, pm-jira, pm-linear, pm-presets, pm-slack, pm-slack-standup, pm-starter, pm-todos, and pm-ts-starter after toolchain alignment to @unbrained/pm-cli ^2026.6.9 / pm-changelog ^2026.6.8, explicit publishConfig.access=public, and prepublishOnly=release:check. pm-jira CHANGELOG.md regenerated for padded calendar heading drift. Sibling checks also passed for pm-brief, pm-context, pm-graph, and pm-web. Secret/history regex scan across active package repos returned 0 tracked matches and 0 history commits. Dedicated gitleaks/trufflehog/detect-secrets binaries were not installed."
